<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Premium Demo | Love Crafted Digital</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="assets/favicon.svg">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/demo-premium.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="overlay">
    <div class="wrap">
      <header>
        <div class="logo">
          <img src="assets/logo-lovecrafted-digital.png" alt="Love Crafted Digital" class="logo-img">
          <span class="logo-text">Premium layout</span>
        </div>
        <nav>
          <a href="#experience">Experience</a>
          <a href="#brand">Brand System</a>
          <a href="#merch">Merch</a>
          <a href="index.html">Main site</a>
        </nav>
      </header>

      <main>
        <section class="hero" id="experience">
          <div>
            <div class="eyebrow">Full brand + website experience</div>
            <h1>High-end western-modern designs that feel like a custom studio build.</h1>
            <p class="lede">
              The premium level is for brands ready to step into a full visual system: custom layouts, polished storytelling,
              merch-ready graphics, and a website that actually feels like your brand.
            </p>
          </div>

          <aside class="hero-board">
            <div class="board-top">
              <div class="board-title">Sample premium project</div>
              <div class="badge">Web + Brand + Merch</div>
            </div>
            <div class="metrics">
              <div class="metric">
                <div class="metric-label">Timeline</div>
                <div class="metric-value">6–8 weeks</div>
                <div class="metric-note">Strategy, design, build, and launch.</div>
              </div>
              <div class="metric">
                <div class="metric-label">Deliverables</div>
                <div class="metric-value">Site + Brand</div>
                <div class="metric-note">Website + logo suite + system.</div>
              </div>
              <div class="metric">
                <div class="metric-label">Extras</div>
                <div class="metric-value">Merch Ready</div>
                <div class="metric-note">Mockups for shirts, hats, stickers.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </aside>
        </section>

        <section id="brand">
          <h2>What the brand system can include</h2>
          <div class="two-col">
            <ul class="list">
              <li><div class="icon">✓</div><span><strong>Logo suite:</strong> primary logo, secondary marks, and a simplified cattle-brand icon.</span></li>
              <li><div class="icon">✓</div><span><strong>Color palette:</strong> earthy neutrals with a bold blue anchor and gold accent tones.</span></li>
              <li><div class="icon">✓</div><span><strong>Type system:</strong> serif + sans pairing that nods to western typography without going full novelty.</span></li>
              <li><div class="icon">✓</div><span><strong>Usage guide:</strong> simple PDF explaining how to use your new visuals consistently.</span></li>
            </ul>
            <div class="panel">
              This demo is all about vibe and structure. When we build your actual project, the content will come from your brand—your story, your voice, your photos.
              The goal is a system that looks premium but still feels approachable and real.
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="merch">
          <h2>Merch & touchpoints</h2>
          <div class="two-col">
            <div class="panel">
              <p class="panel-copy">
                Premium projects can include artwork ready for:
              </p>
              <ul class="list">
                <li><div class="icon">✓</div><span>Front and back t-shirt designs with your mark and tagline.</span></li>
                <li><div class="icon">✓</div><span>Hat patches or embroidery-friendly versions of your logo.</span></li>
                <li><div class="icon">✓</div><span>Sticker-ready files you can send straight to your printer.</span></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="panel">
              <p class="panel-copy">
                Photo shoots for these touchpoints can be subcontracted and planned around your budget and location.
                You’ll get direction on what shots to capture and how they’ll plug back into your website and socials once everything is ready.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </main>

      <footer>
        © <span id="year"></span> Love Crafted Digital — Premium Demo
      </footer>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    document.getElementById("year").textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
